1.2.name: wordpress/navigation-menu-ids-classes
1.2.description:
This plug-in limits the classes WordPress added to navigation menus to only those desired by the Theme owner, adds a unique ID to each li and removes any empty class attributes.

More about this plug-in can be found at: http://aarontgrogg.com/2011/09/28/wordpress-plug-in-navigation-menu-ids-classes/

Please let me know if you have any questions/suggestions/thoughts,

Atg http://aarontgrogg.com/ aarontgrogg@gmail.com
